%% POST /api/channels/:id/messages 全链路 —— seq 原子分配 + 跨 pod 扇出
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor S as Sender
    participant H as HTTP handler
    participant MS as MessageService
    participant MR as MessageRepo
    participant CR as ChannelRepo
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant Fan as pushToMembers<br/>(goroutine)
    participant Pusher as hubMessagePusher
    participant Hub as Hub (本 pod)
    participant XPod as CrossPodPush

    S->>H: POST /api/channels/42/messages<br/>{content, client_msg_id}
    H->>MS: SendMessage(SendParams{...})
    MS->>CR: GetMember(42, uid)  ← 鉴权
    CR-->>MS: member
    MS->>MR: Send(ctx, msg)

    MR->>DB: BEGIN
    alt client_msg_id 非空
        MR->>DB: SELECT id, seq FROM messages<br/>WHERE channel_id=? AND client_msg_id=?
        DB-->>MR: 命中 → return 原 id/seq (幂等短路)
    end

    Note over MR,DB: AllocSeqAndInsert (tx 复用):
    MR->>DB: UPDATE channels SET last_seq=last_seq+1<br/>WHERE id=42 RETURNING last_seq
    DB-->>MR: seq=131 (行锁保证原子)
    MR->>DB: INSERT messages (channel_id=42, seq=131, ...)
    DB-->>MR: msg.ID

    alt VisibleTo 非空 (directed)
        MR->>CR: IncrementPhantomCount(chID, visibleWithSender)
        CR->>DB: UPDATE channel_members SET phantom_count+=1<br/>WHERE channel_id=42 AND user_id NOT IN (...)
    end
    MR->>DB: COMMIT

    MR-->>MS: msg (with seq=131)
    MS-->>H: msg
    H-->>S: 201 msg
    H->>Fan: go pushToMembers(msg) (异步 background ctx)

    Fan->>MS: ListMembers(42)
    MS-->>Fan: [m1, m2, m3, ...]
    loop 对每个成员 m
        Fan->>Pusher: PushMessage(m.UserID, msg or phantom)
        Pusher->>XPod: dispatch(m.UserID, TypePushMsg, payload)
        XPod->>Hub: hub.PushToUser(m.UserID)
        alt 本 pod 命中
            Hub-->>XPod: sent > 0 → return
        else 本 pod miss
            XPod->>XPod: Lookup routing → 远端 pod 列表<br/>投递 Pulsar (见 01-cross-pod-push.mmd)
        end
    end
